# Gemini CLI Project Instructions

- **Automatic Sync:** After completing any code modification or file operation, the agent MUST execute `.\git-sync.bat` to push changes to GitHub.
- **Commit Message:** Use the standard message "Update NewsHub".
- **Port Convention:** The application runs on Port 8080 (behind Nginx) or Port 80 (standalone). Current setup: Standalone Port 80.
- **Environment:** Java 21 Spring Boot.
